query:
SELECT log.file_info_id 
             FROM file_sync_log log
             INNER JOIN (
                SELECT file_info_id, MAX(id) AS max_id
                FROM file_sync_log
                GROUP BY file_info_id
             ) latest ON log.file_info_id = latest.file_info_id AND log.id = latest.max_id
             WHERE log.status = ?
